{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f3076f7973","title":"关于大批判问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d92603243b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"f3076f7973"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33c539c7f3","type":"title","text":"关于大批判问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"7837e796a7","type":"paragraph","text":"批判文章不要像九评那样长，每篇一二千字，不要超过三千字。一篇一个中心，一个概念，明明白白。长了就没有人看，记不住。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"7d813bc531","type":"paragraph","text":"同意。团结和服从都是有条件的，不是无条件的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"d248130de0","type":"paragraph","text":"年纪大的、年纪中的、年纪小的也要“三结合”，不要看不起年轻人。二十几岁、三十几岁的人都能做工作。搞“三结合”，要老中小，老的都会去见上帝的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"977190eb46","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布、粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。批判文章文字要短。彭、罗、陆、杨可以提为反革命修正主义，其他人都称修正主义分子。中国的赫鲁晓夫在文章中提，在标题上要提","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"d52e74467d","type":"paragraph","text":"大批判要慎重，要确实，要调查清楚。调查清楚，批判才有力量，否则就会一风吹。引他（指刘少奇）的话不能只顾头不顾尾。批判要站得住。“托拉斯”这个名词，不能一概驳，主要驳他走资本主义道路。有些旧名词要赋予新的意义","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"2aaf985370","type":"paragraph","text":"“狮服工具论”要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律。服从、团结，那是有条件的。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"},{"id":"83ff968f94","type":"paragraph","text":"写文章要琢磨，要准确，要尖锐明确","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973"}],"page":{"id":"45db71e349","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f3076f7973","start":451,"end":451}}}},"__N_SSG":true}